{"tid":1944191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有線中國組 - 武漢漢口殯儀館外現人龍領取病逝親屬骨灰","createTime":"2020-03-26T08:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T08:54:59.000Z","uid":33456,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5d902907a95a904564c028bf273d8b58ae7ce304","tid":1944191,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"【武漢漢口殯儀館外現人龍】<br />\n【領取病逝親屬骨灰】<br />\n內地有網民上載了一張武漢漢口殯儀館的相片，可以見到殯儀館外有長長人龍。門口有指示牌，寫著是要領取疫情期間死亡親人的骨灰，但照片很快就被刪除。<br />\n有另一名網民指，現場保安嚴密，到處都是便衣，只要一舉起手機就會有人制止。有家屬抱著遺照等待，有人抱著骨灰盒走過，人很多，很安靜，沒有哀樂，也沒有哭聲。<br />\n武漢黃陂城管亦發文指，已安排人手為發放骨灰行動加強環境秩序保障。<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n#武漢<br />\n#新型肺炎<br />\n#殯儀館<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/2486962154781589\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fposts%2F2486962154781589&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=837ec73b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/2486962154781589</a><br />\n<br />\n3盒，Thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6066cac454a621271194a13095e96354f31e06c6","tid":1944191,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"原來講得多nmsl真係有報應，連登仔好積下口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e245e01fa0f9ab889790705a7575b14941c12d","tid":1944191,"uid":164845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:44:13.000Z","msg":"捧返去啲骨灰都唔知邊個嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e306becca99d0058c8f14e4a018e4144faf87bb3","tid":1944191,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"有線高層好仆街。但前線記者好野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可唔可幫推呢幾個post，唔明點解全部沉底<br />\n<br />\n原來支那入境係冇手帶！屌你老母林鄭月娥<br />\n- 分享